description:
You will become a real interior designer specializing in kitchens. Your creative vision and problem-solving skills will be put to the test as you will need to arrange furniture and other items in the limited kitchen space, creating a cozy and functional environment.

The game provides a wide selection of kitchen furniture. You can experiment with different styles and create unique designs. And with a variety of tableware, from elegant porcelain sets to colorful ceramic bowls, you can add some flair to your project.

But remember that space is limited! You'll need to be smart to make the most of every inch of your kitchen. Arrange furniture to provide ample room for movement and create a comfortable work area. Every decision you make will impact the overall functionality and aesthetics of your kitchen.

The game offers creative freedom and the satisfaction of creating a beautiful and functional space. So let your design imagination run wild and you can turn ordinary kitchens into stunning masterpieces!

GAME FEATURES:
• An excellent warm-up for attentiveness and ingenuity;
• Many different types of furniture and cutlery;
• Exciting gameplay for all ages;
